  <brief_title>The Impact of Vitamin on the Clinical Course in Cases Infected by Novel H1N1 Influenza Virus A</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Vitamin on the Clinical Course in Cases Infected by Novel H1N1 Influenza Virus A: a Randomized-controlled Trial</official_title>
