  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt; 20 years

          -  Acute respiratory illness suspected H1N1 infection

          -  Acute febrile respiratory illness(BT &gt; 37.8) and throat pain or cough or nasal
             congestion

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Hypersensitivity to vitamin A

          -  History of liver disease or renal disease

          -  Urinary stone disease
      </textblock>
